        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\n!theme plain\nskinparam defaultFontName Arial\nskinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #ffffff\nskinparam ActivityBorderColor #000000\nskinparam ConditionEndStyle hline\nskinparam SwimlaneBorderColor #000000\n\ntitle Activity Diagram: Transaction History Explorer\\n(Pet Treatment Campaign)\n\n|User|\nstart\n:Navigate to \&quot;Transaction Explorer\&quot; page;\n:Select Filter Mode\\n(All Transactions, Specific User, Specific Campaign);\n\n|Pet Treatment dApp|\n:Initialize Data Fetch State\\n(Show Loading Spinner);\n\nfork\n    |Data Layer (RPC &amp; Supabase)|\n    partition \&quot;Off-Chain Query (Supabase)\&quot; {\n        :Query &#39;donations&#39; &amp; &#39;refunds&#39; tables;\n        :Fetch User Profiles (Wallet to Name mapping);\n        :Fetch Campaign Metadata (Titles);\n    }\nfork again\n    |Data Layer (RPC &amp; Supabase)|\n    partition \&quot;On-Chain Query (Hardhat RPC)\&quot; {\n        :Wagmi publicClient.getLogs()\\nFetch &#39;DonationRecorded&#39; Events;\n        :Wagmi publicClient.getLogs()\\nFetch &#39;RefundIssued&#39; Events;\n    }\nend fork\n\n|Pet Treatment dApp|\n:Merge &amp; Enrich Data:\\nCross-reference immutable on-chain logs\\nwith off-chain human-readable names;\n:Apply active UI filters\\n(Search queries / Date ranges);\n:Calculate Platform Metrics\\n(Total Volume ETH, Transaction Count);\n:Render Etherscan-style\\nunified Transaction Ledger;\n\n|User|\n:View verified platform activity\\nand CFR reward history;\nstop\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="d4WOsVZWoGXvF_kk4NiG-50">
